text: Hi, can you help me delete a meeting reservation?
Sure, I can assist you with that. What's the meeting topic and start time?
The meeting topic is "New Employee Orientation" and the start time is "2023-03-27 09:00:00".
Alright, let me check if I have your token. Can you please provide me with your username and password?
My username is "newuser" and my password is "newpass".
Thank you. I have received your token. Now, can you also provide me with the end time, location, and attendees of the meeting?
The end time is "2023-03-27 11:00:00", the location is "Training Room", and the attendees are "David Wang", "Amy Chen", and "Erica Liu".
Alright, I have successfully deleted your meeting reservation.
